{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"onLaunched","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConnectFlags","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"@escaping"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"text":"AppLaunchContextRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO19AppLaunchContextRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AppLaunchContextRef"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/AppInfoRef","text":"AppInfoRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO10AppInfoRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Flags","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"handler","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"launched"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Because a launch operation may involve spawning multiple instances of the","type":"text"},{"typ